4145 if (XBIT(124, 0x100000)) { /* If skip comments... */
4146 *tokval = 0;
4147 p = lineptr;
4148 while (*p != '\n')
4149 ++p;
4150 if ((i = p - lineptr) >= TOKMAX - 1)
4151 i = TOKMAX - 1;
4152 strncpy(tokval, lineptr, i);
4153 tokval[i] = 0;
4154 lineptr = p;
4155 retval = c;
4156 goto nextok_ret;
4157 }
4158 /* Fall thru if we do not have a C or c in the first column */
4159 }
4160 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
4161
4162 case 'A':
4163 case 'B': /* case 'C': */
4164 case 'D':
4165 case 'E':
4166 case 'F':
4167 case 'G':
4168 case 'H':
4169 case 'I':
4170 case 'J':
4171 case 'K': /* case 'L': */
4172 case 'M':
4173 case 'N':
4174 case 'O':
4175 case 'P':
4176 case 'Q':
4177 case 'R':
4178 case 'S':
4179 case 'T':
4180 case 'U':
4181 case 'V':
4182 case 'W':
4183 case 'X':
4184 case 'Y':
4185 case 'Z':
4186 case '_':
4187 case 'a':
4188 case 'b':
4189 /* case 'c': */ case 'd':
4190 case 'e':
4191 case 'f':
4192 case 'g':
4193 case 'h':
4194 case 'i':
4195 case 'j':
4196 case 'k':
4197 case 'l':
4198 case 'm':
4199 case 'n':
4200 case 'o':
4201 case 'p':
4202 case 'q':
4203 case 'r':
4204 case 's':
4205 case 't':
4206 case 'u':
4207 case 'v':
4208 case 'w':
4209 case 'x':
4210 case 'y':
4211 case 'z':
4212 /* we know the whole identifier must be in the buffer */
4213 p = lineptr;
4214 retval = T_IDENT;
4215 ident:
4216 while (isident(*p++))
4217 /* NULL */;
4218 --p;
4219 if ((i = p - lineptr) >= TOKMAX - 1) {
4220 pperr(212, 3);
4221 i = TOKMAX - 1;
4222 }
4223 strncpy(tokval, lineptr, i);
4224 tokval[i] = 0;
4225 lineptr = p;
4226 goto nextok_ret;
4227
4228 case 'L':
4229 p = lineptr;
4230 if (*p != '"' && *p != '\'') {
4231 retval = T_IDENT;
4232 goto ident;
4233 }
4234 delim = *p;
4235 i = 2;
4236 ++p;
4237 *tokval++ = delim;
4238 ++lineptr;
4239 toktyp = (delim == '"') ? T_WSTRING : T_WCHAR;
4240 goto wchar;
4241
4242 case '0':
4243 case '1':
4244 case '2':
4245 case '3':
4246 case '4':
4247 case '5':
4248 case '6':
4249 case '7':
4250 case '8':
4251 case '9':
4252 /* a number */
4253 /* must all be in buffer */
4254 p = lineptr;
4255 dotnum:
4256 dot_seen=0;
4257 for (;;) {
4258 if (*p == 'E' || *p == 'e') {
4259 ++p;
4260 if (*p == '+' || *p == '-')
4261 ++p;
4262 } else if (*p == 'P' || *p == 'p') {
4263 ++p;
4264 if (*p == '+' || *p == '-')
4265 ++p;
4266 } else if (*p == '.' && !dot_seen) {
4267 ++p;
4268 dot_seen=1;
4269 } else if (isident(*p))
4270 ++p;
4271 else
4272 break;
4273 }
4274 if ((i = p - lineptr) >= TOKMAX - 1) {
4275 pperr(220, 3);
4276 i = TOKMAX - 1;
4277 }
4278
4279 strncpy(tokval, lineptr, i);
4280 tokval[i] = 0;
4281 toktyp = T_PPNUM;
4282 lineptr = p;
4283 retval = toktyp;
4284 goto nextok_ret;
4285
4286 case '.':
4287 p = lineptr;
4288 if (asm_mode) {
4289 retval = T_IDENT;
4290 goto ident;
4291 }
4292 if (p >= lineend) {
4293 goto dotdone;
4294 }
4295 if (isdig(*p)) {
4296 goto dotnum;
4297 }
4298 if (*p == '.') {
4299 ++p;
4300 if (p >= lineend) {
4301 goto dotdone;
4302 }
4303 if (*p != '.')
4304 goto dotdone;
4305 lineptr = ++p;
4306 *tokval++ = '.';
4307 *tokval++ = '.';
4308 *tokval = 0;
4309 retval = T_OP;
4310 goto nextok_ret;
4311 }
4312 dotdone:
4313 *tokval = 0;
4314 retval = '.';
4315 goto nextok_ret;
4316
4317 case '>': /* >=, >>, >>= */
4318 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4319 goto defret;
4320 if (*lineptr == '=')
4321 goto twocop;
4322 if (*lineptr == '>') {
4323 if (lineptr + 1 >= lineend)
4324 goto twocop;
4325 if (*++lineptr == '=') {
4326 *tokval++ = '>';
4327 *tokval++ = '=';
4328 ++lineptr;
4329 *tokval = 0;
4330 retval = T_OP;
4331 goto nextok_ret;
4332 } else {
4333 --lineptr;
4334 goto twocop;
4335 }
4336 }
4337 goto defret;
4338 case '<': /* <=, <<, <<= */
4339 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4340 goto defret;
4341 if (*lineptr == '=')
4342 goto twocop;
4343 if (*lineptr == '<') {
4344 if (lineptr + 1 >= lineend)
4345 goto twocop;
4346 if (*++lineptr == '=') {
4347 *tokval++ = '<';
4348 *tokval++ = '=';
4349 ++lineptr;
4350 *tokval = 0;
4351 retval = T_OP;
4352 goto nextok_ret;
4353 } else {
4354 --lineptr;
4355 goto twocop;
4356 }
4357 }
4358 goto defret;
4359 case '!': /* != */
4360 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4361 goto defret;
4362 if (*lineptr == '=')
4363 goto twocop;
4364 if (asm_mode) {
4365 if (*lineptr == '+' || *lineptr == '-')
4366 goto twocop;
4367 }
4368 in_ftn_comment = TRUE;
4369 if (XBIT(124, 0x100000)) { /* If skip comments is set */
4370 p = lineptr;
4371 while (*p != '\n')
4372 ++p;
4373 if ((i = p - lineptr) >= TOKMAX - 1) {
4374 i = TOKMAX - 1;
4375 }
4376 strncpy(tokval, lineptr, i);
4377 tokval[i] = 0;
4378 lineptr = p;
4379 retval = c;
4380 goto nextok_ret;
4381 }
4382 goto defret;
4383 case '+': /* ++, += */
4384 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4385 goto defret;
4386 if (*lineptr == '=' || *lineptr == '+')
4387 goto twocop;
4388 if (asm_mode) {
4389 if (*lineptr == '!')
4390 goto twocop; /* +! */
4391 }
4392 goto defret;
4393 case '-': /* --, -=, -> */
4394 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4395 goto defret;
4396 if (*lineptr == '=' || *lineptr == '-' || *lineptr == '>')
4397 goto twocop;
4398 if (asm_mode) {
4399 if (*lineptr == '!')
4400 goto twocop; /* -! */
4401 }
4402 goto defret;
4403 case '@':
4404 if (asm_mode) {
4405 if (lineptr < lineend && *lineptr == '(')
4406 goto twocop; /* @( */
4407 p = lineptr;
4408 retval = T_IDENT;
4409 goto ident;
4410 }
4411 goto defret;
4412 case '%': /* %= */
4413 if (asm_mode) {
4414 p = lineptr;
4415 retval = T_IDENT;
4416 goto ident;
4417 }
4418 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4419 goto defret;
4420 if (*lineptr == '=')
4421 goto twocop;
4422 goto defret;
4423 case '&': /* &&, &= */
4424 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4425 goto defret;
4426 if (*lineptr == '=' || *lineptr == '&')
4427 goto twocop;
4428 goto defret;
4429 case '*': /* *= */
4430 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4431 goto defret;
4432 if (*lineptr == '=')
4433 goto twocop;
4434 if (!flg.freeform && lineptr == linebuf + LINELEN + 1)
4435 {
4436 /* * in column 1, start of old-style comment */
4437 /* everything to end of line is a comment */
4438 if (XBIT(124, 0x100000)) { /* If skip comments... */
4439 *tokval = 0;
4440 p = lineptr;
4441 while (*p != '\n')
4442 ++p;
4443 if ((i = p - lineptr) >= TOKMAX - 1)
4444 i = TOKMAX - 1;
4445 strncpy(tokval, lineptr, i);
4446 tokval[i] = 0;
4447 lineptr = p;
4448 retval = c;
4449 goto nextok_ret;
4450 }
4451 }
4452 goto defret;
4453 case '=': /* == */
4454 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4455 goto defret;
4456 if (*lineptr == '=')
4457 goto twocop;
4458 goto defret;
4459 case '^': /* ^= */
4460 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4461 goto defret;
4462 if (*lineptr == '=')
4463 goto twocop;
4464 goto defret;
4465 case '|': /* ||, |= */
4466 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4467 goto defret;
4468 if (*lineptr == '=' || *lineptr == '|')
4469 goto twocop;
4470 goto defret;
4471 case '#':
4472 if (!in_dodef && !flg.freeform && (lineptr != linebuf + LINELEN + 1))
4473 {
4474 /* Fixed form and not initial/first column, then skip.
4475 * This means that all preprocessor macro '#' tokens
4476 * in fixed-form must begin in column 1.
4477 * The line is passed onto the backend.
4478 */
4479 *tokval = 0;
4480 p = lineptr;
4481 while (*p != '\n')
4482 ++p; /* Advance to end of line */
4483
4484 /* Skip the line if in a false branch of a macro conditional */
4485 if (ifstack(truth) == FALSE) {
4486 lineptr = p;
4487 retval = '\n';
4488 goto nextok_ret;
4489 }
4490
4491 if ((i = p - lineptr) >= TOKMAX - 1)
4492 i = TOKMAX - 1;
4493 strncpy(tokval, lineptr, i);
4494 tokval[i] = 0;
4495
4496 /* If not in a fixed-form comment, then pass line to rest of
4497 * compiler. Else we are in a fixed-form comment and might be
4498 * passing the data following # twice.
4499 */
4500 tmp = *(linebuf + LINELEN); /* First character in column 1 */
4501 if (!(tmp == '*' || tmp == 'c' || tmp == 'C' || tmp == '!'))
4502 ptok(&tokval[-1]);
4503 lineptr = p;
4504 retval = c;
4505 goto nextok_ret;
4506 }
4507 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4508 goto defret;
4509 if (*lineptr == '#') {
4510 ++lineptr;
4511 *tokval++ = '#';
4512 *tokval++ = 0;
4513 retval = T_CONCAT;
4514 goto nextok_ret;
4515 }
4516 goto defret;
4517 twocop:
4518 *tokval++ = *lineptr++;
4519 *tokval = 0;
4520 retval = T_OP;
4521 goto nextok_ret;
4522
4523 case '"':
4524 case '\'':
4525 delim = c;
4526 i = 1;
4527 p = lineptr;
4528 toktyp = T_STRING;
4529
4530 wchar:
4531 while (p < lineend && *p != '\n') {
4532 if (*p == delim)
4533 break;
4534 if (*p == (char)ENDTOKEN) {
4535 --p;
4536 break;
4537 }
4538 if (*p == '\\') {
4539 ++p;
4540 if (p >= lineend || *p == '\n')
4541 break;
4542 }
4543 ++p;
4544 }
4545
4546 /* If the line is unterminated (no closing quote)
4547 * Note: Fortran, we do not error here as this might be a Fortran
4548 * comment we are scanning. Instead, the Fortran lexer will error if
4549 * necessary.
4550 */
4551 if (p >= lineend || *p == '\n') {
4552 if (XBIT(122, 2) && flg.es) /* -Xs and -E/-P */
4553 ;
4554 } else
4555 ++p;
4556 /* copy to tokval */
4557 if ((i += p - lineptr) >= TOKMAX) {
4558 pperr(223, 4);
4559 *tokval = 0;
4560 } else {
4561 strncpy(tokval, lineptr, p - lineptr);
4562 tokval[p - lineptr] = 0;
4563 lineptr = p;
4564 }
4565 retval = toktyp;
4566 goto nextok_ret;
4567 /* NOTREACHED */;
4568
4569 case '/': /* /*, //, /= */
4570 if (lineptr >= lineend)
4571 goto defret;
4572 if (*lineptr == '=')
4573 goto twocop;
4574
4575 /* -B or -c9x options: Ignore C++ style comments "//" to end-of-line */
4576 p = lineptr;
4577 if (cpp_comments && *lineptr == '/') {
4578 while (lineptr < lineend && *lineptr != '\n')
4579 ++lineptr;
4580
4581 /* -C option: Pass comments through the preprocessor */
4582 if (XBIT(123, 1) && flg.es == TRUE && ifstack(truth)) {
4583 i = lineptr - p;
4584 if (i > TOKMAX) /* Truncate comment if too long */
4585 i = TOKMAX;
4586 strncpy(tokval, p, i);
4587 tokval[i] = 0;
4588 ptok(&tokval[-1]);
4589 }
4590
4591 /* comment is a space */
4592 --tokval;
4593 *tokval++ = ' ';
4594 *tokval = 0;
4595 retval = ' ';
4596 if (XBIT(122, 2)) {
4597 --tokval;
4598 goto again;
4599 }
4600 goto nextok_ret;
4601 }
4602
4603 if (*lineptr != '*')
4604 goto defret;
4605 --tokval;
4606
4607 /* Save start of comment (in case of -C option) */
4608 comment_ptr = lineptr - 1;
4609
4610 lineptr++; /* Bypass the '*' */
4611 for (;;) {
4612 p = lineptr;
4613 /* scan to end of line or '*' */
4614 while (p < lineend && *p != '*')
4615 ++p;
4616
4617 if (p >= lineend) {
4618 /* -C option: Pass comments through the preprocessor */
4619 if (XBIT(123, 1) && flg.es == TRUE && ifstack(truth)) {
4620 i = p - comment_ptr;
4621 if (i > TOKMAX) /* Truncate comment if too long */
4622 i = TOKMAX;
4623 strncpy(tokval, comment_ptr, i);
4624 tokval[i - 1] = 0;
4625 tokval = savtokval;
4626 ptok(tokval);
4627 }
4628 if (p == lineend && in_ftn_comment) {
4629 goto defret;
4630 }
4631 ptok("\n");
4632 popstack();
4633 if (_nextline() == EOF) {
4634 pperr(208, 3);
4635 *tokval = 0;
4636 retval = EOF;
4637 goto nextok_ret;
4638 }
4639 --lineptr;
4640 comment_ptr = lineptr;
4641 continue;
4642 }
4643 if (p > lineptr && p[-1] == '/') /* possible nested comment */
4644 pperr(244, 1);
4645 if (*++p == '/') {
4646 /* -C option: Pass comments through the preprocessor */
4647 if (XBIT(123, 1) && flg.es == TRUE && ifstack(truth)) {
4648 i = p - comment_ptr + 1;
4649 if (i > TOKMAX) /* Truncate comment if too long */
4650 i = TOKMAX;
4651 strncpy(tokval, comment_ptr, i);
4652 tokval[i] = 0;
4653 tokval = savtokval;
4654 ptok(tokval);
4655 }
4656
4657 lineptr = p + 1;
4658 /* comment is a space */
4659 retval = ' ';
4660 *tokval++ = ' ';
4661 *tokval = 0;
4662 if (XBIT(122, 2)) {
4663 --tokval;
4664 goto again;
4665 }
4666 goto nextok_ret;
4667 }
4668
4669 lineptr = p;
4670 }
4671 /* NOTREACHED */;
4672
4673 case '\r':
4674 if (XBIT(50, 0x20) || *lineptr != '\n') {
4675 /* not DOS end-of-line */
4676 *tokval++ = ' ';
4677 }
4678 retval = ' ';
4679 *tokval = 0;
4680 goto nextok_ret;
4681
4682 default:
4683 switch (MASK(c)) {
4684 case SENTINEL:
4685 retval = T_SENTINEL;
4686 *tokval = 0;
4687 goto nextok_ret;
4688 case NOFUNC:
4689 retval = T_NOFIDENT;
4690 --tokval;
4691 p = lineptr;
4692 goto ident;
4693 case NOSUBST:
4694 retval = T_NSIDENT;
4695 --tokval;
4696 p = lineptr;
4697 goto ident;
4698 case ENDTOKEN:
4699 --tokval;
4700 goto again;
4701 case WHITESPACE:
4702 --tokval;
4703 goto again;
4704 default:
4705 break;
4706 }
4707 /***** fall thru *****/
4708 defret:
4709 *tokval = 0;
4710 retval = c;
4711 goto nextok_ret;
4712 } /* switch */
4713
4714nextok_ret:
4715
4716 popstack();
4717 return (retval);
4718}

4720static int
4721_nextline(void)
4722{
4723 static int lastinc = 0;
4724 FILE *fp;
4725 char *p;
4726 int i;
4727 int c;
4728 int j;
4729 int firstime;
4730 int dojoin;
4731 char *start;
4732 char *savestart;
4733 ptrdiff_t diff;
4734 int isquest;
4735 char buffer[133];
4736 char *fn;
4737
4738again:
4739 fp = ifp;
4740 lineptr = linebuf + linelen;
4741 startline = inclstack[inclev].lineno;
4742 if ((c = getc(fp)) == EOF) {
4743 if (inclev <= 0)
4744 return (EOF);
4745 fn = inclstack[inclev].fname;
4746 for (i = 0; i < inclev - 1; i++) {
4747 if (!strcmp(inclstack[i].fname, fn)) {
4748 --inclstack[i].count;
4749 break;
4750 }
4751 }
4752 fclose(ifp);
4753 --inclev;
4754 gbl.curr_file = inclstack[inclev].fname;
4755 ifp = inclstack[inclev].ifp;
4756 idir.last = inclstack[inclev].path_idx;
4757 strcpy(cur_fname, inclstack[inclev].fname);
4758 cur_from_stdinc = inclstack[inclev].from_stdinc;
4759 pr_line(gbl.curr_file, inclstack[inclev].lineno, cur_from_stdinc);
4760 goto again;
4761 }
4762
4763 i = 0;
4764 firstime = 1;
4765 savestart = start = lineptr;
4766
4767joinlines:
4768 p = start;
4769 dojoin = 0;
4770 isquest = 0;
4771
4772 while (c != EOF && c != '\n') {
4773 if (p - linebuf > linesize - 2) {
4774 diff = realloc_linebuf(0);
4775 start += diff;
4776 savestart += diff;
4777 p += diff;
4778 }
4779 *p++ = c;
4780 if ((c = getc(fp)) == '?')
4781 isquest = 1;
4782 ++i;
4783 }
4784
4785 /* Decide to join lines or not */
4786 if (c == '\n') {
4787 /* tpr 1359 - don't join lines for fortran */
4788 /* tpr 1405 - need to join lines if a preprocessor directive */
4789 if (p > lineptr && lineptr[0] == '#' && c == '\n' && p[-1] == '\\') {
4790 /* join <return> lines */
4791 start = p - 1;
4792 dojoin = 1;
4793 }
4794 }
4795
4796 *p++ = '\n';
4797 *p = '\0';
4798 lineend = p;
4799
4800 if (lastinc <= inclev) {
4801 ++inclstack[inclev].lineno;
4802 if (firstime)
4803 ++startline;
4804 }
4805 lastinc = inclev;
4806 if (list_flag && (flg.include || inclev == 0)) {
4807 if (inclev == 0)
4808 sprintf(buffer, "(%5d) ", inclstack[inclev].lineno);
4809 else
4810 sprintf(buffer, "(*%04d) ", inclstack[inclev].lineno);
4811 j = (p - savestart) - 1;
4812 if (j >= 132 - 8) {
4813 strncpy(&buffer[8], savestart, 132 - 8);
4814 buffer[132] = 0;
4815 } else {
4816 strcpy(&buffer[8], savestart);
4817 buffer[j + 8] = 0;
4818 }
4819 list_line(buffer);
4820 }
4821 if (dojoin) {
4822 firstime = 0;
4823 savestart = start;
4824 c = getc(fp);
4825 goto joinlines;
4826 }
4827 return *lineptr++;
4828}

4830static ptrdiff_t
4831realloc_linebuf(ptrdiff_t extra)
4832{
4833 char *old_linebuf;
4834 int old_linesize;
4835 int i;
4836 ptrdiff_t diff;
4837
4838 if (extra < LINELEN)
4839 extra = LINELEN;
4840 old_linebuf = linebuf;
4841 old_linesize = linesize;
4842
4843 /* Aquire a new line buffer */
4844 linelen += extra;
4845 linesize = (2 * linelen);
4846 NEW(linebuf, char, linesize);
4847
4848 /* Allocate HALF of the new memory at the beginning and HALF at the end */
4849 memcpy(linebuf + extra, old_linebuf, old_linesize);
4850
4851 /* Calculate the difference in location of linebuf's. */
4852 diff = linebuf + extra - old_linebuf;
4853
4854 /* Adjust linebuf pointers in macro stack area */
4855 for (i = 0; i <= macstk_top; ++i)
4856 macstk[i].sav_lptr += diff;
4857
4858 /* Adjust linebuf pointers to new area */
4859 lineptr += diff;
4860 lineend += diff;
4861 savlptr += diff;
4862
4863 FREE(old_linebuf);
4864
4865 return (diff);
4866}
